UJG91OP  TITLE  'USER EXIT FOR JCL CARDS'
* THIS LOAD MODULE IS ENTERED JUST BEFORE A JCL CARD IS OUTPUT
*  TO THE JCL FILE.
* ALL JCL CARDS (COMMENTS INCLUDED) COME THROUGH THIS ROUTINE,
*  BUT DATA CARDS DO NOT.
*
* ON ENTRY, R1 POINTS DIRECTLY AT THE STRING TO GO OUT.
*
* NOTE:- THE FIRST 2 BYTES OF THE STRING CONTAIN THE LENGTH OF
*  THE STRING
           SPACE 3
           PRINT OFF
           COPY JOLCOM
           PRINT ON,DATA
           JOLSAVE CSECT=UJG91OP
           JOLRETN RC=0
           END
